\begin_layout Section
Hicksian vs.
 Walrasian Demand
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Recall from our discussion on duality that the following must hold: 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{h}^{*}(\vec{p},\bar{u})=\vec{x}^{*}(\vec{p},e(\vec{p},\bar{u}))$
\end_inset

