\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\partial x_{i}(\vec{p},w)}{\partial p_{i}}=\frac{\partial h_{i}(\vec{p},\bar{u})}{\partial p_{i}}-\frac{\partial x_{i}(\vec{p},w)}{\partial w}\times x_{i}(\vec{p},w)$
\end_inset

.
